data.description: Incredible Brooklyn Park end unit townhome in Sumter Manor. These units are rarely offered for sale. 3BRs on one level with full bath. Main level has large living room and spacious kitchen with newer stainless appliances with tons of cabinet space. Formal dining room. Main level in-unit laundry. Over-sized one car garage. Walk-out patio allow easy access for pets, grilling and entertainment. Recently refreshed with newer carpeting in two rooms and fresh coat of paint. Quick move-in available. See 3D virtual tour for your own private showing today!
